evolution-data-server-3.16.3-2.fc22.x86_64
evolution-ews-3.16.3-1.fc22.x86_64
evolution-data-server-debuginfo-3.12.11-2.fc21.x86_64

How reproducible:
Seemingly at random.

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Create new message/reply/forward.
2.
3.

Actual results:
Occasionally the color of the text is autoselected as light gray, sometimes default black.


Expected results:
Always black (or whatever the default is set to).

Additional info:
Thanks for a bug report. This had been filled recently, as bug #1229841, and will be fixed with the upcoming evolution 3.16.4, according to the associated upstream bug report.

